revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Plat_UpNearestWaitDownStay}}
{{Special|172|tag, speed, delay|Platform|UpNearestWaitDownStay}}

* ''tag'': Tag of affected sector 
* ''speed'': Speed of move 
* ''delay'': Tics before going back down 

Raises the tagged sector's floor to the height of the next-highest neighboring floor, waits for ''delay'' [[Definitions|tics]], then lowers to its original height.

